headline: Rockwell Automation to Report Fourth Quarter Fiscal 2025 Results
summary: MILWAUKEE, October 23, 2025--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) is scheduled to report its fourth quarter and full year fiscal 2025 results as well as introduce fiscal 2026 guidance on Thursday, Nov. 6, before the market opens. The release will be posted on the Rockwell Investor Relations website at www.rockwellautomation.com/en-us/investors.html.

headline: Should You Reconsider Rockwell Automation After Its 33.7% Jump and New Partnership Updates?
summary: If you are weighing your options on Rockwell Automation stock, you are certainly not alone. The company has caught the attention of both long-term investors and those looking for a timely play, thanks in large part to its impressive recent returns. After all, Rockwell's share price has climbed 24.7% just since January, not to mention a hefty 33.7% rise over the past year.
